cypher_query: MATCH (p:Person)-[:HAS_SKILL]->(s:Skill) WHERE s.name IN ['Python', 'scikit-learn'] WITH DISTINCT p MATCH (p)-[:HAS_SKILL]->(all_s:Skill) RETURN p.name as name, collect(all_s.name) as all_skills ORDER BY name
results: [{"name": "Aisha Williams", "all_skills": ["communication", "collaboration", "analytical skills", "Apache Kafka", "SQL", "Tableau", "Python"]}, {"name": "Marcus Rodriguez", "all_skills": ["collaboration", "problem-solving", "SQL", "Apache Kafka", "REST API", "Python", "AWS", "Redis", "TypeScript", "Node.js", "PostgreSQL"]}]
